{"tid":2229418,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"太平洋群島新喀里多尼亞今天舉行獨立公投 預料再度否決脫離法國獨立","createTime":"2020-10-04T11:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T14:10:41.000Z","uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1670d2f194aae9a680869fd6593cddab8d967b48","tid":2229418,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:34:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/europechinese/1747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Feuropechinese%2F1747&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil9iuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=1626d652\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/europechinese/1747</a><br />\n<br />\n太平洋群島新喀里多尼亞今天舉行獨立公投，根據已點算的七成選票，約53%反對由法國獨立，預料再度否決脫離法國獨立，但反對比率較兩年前上一次公投少了3個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n法國與新喀里多尼亞1998年簽署了協議，後者有權在2018、2020和2022年，各舉行一次獨立公投。<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.lci.fr/politique/nouvelle-caledonie-resultat-referendum-le-non-a-l-independance-l-emporte-de-peu-selon-les-resultats-partiels-du-vote-2166315.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lci.fr%2Fpolitique%2Fnouvelle-caledonie-resultat-referendum-le-non-a-l-independance-l-emporte-de-peu-selon-les-resultats-partiels-du-vote-2166315.html&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil9iuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=4ae35df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lci.fr/politique/nouvelle-caledonie-resultat-referendum-le-non-a-l-independance-l-emporte-de-peu-selon-les-resultats-partiels-du-vote-2166315.html</a>"},{"pid":"9159b0cda8edd7d8ac4f169f9a3b1cfdb178b59f","tid":2229418,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"新喀里多尼亞（法語：Nouvelle-Cal&eacute;donie），位於南回歸線附近，是法國在大洋洲西南部的一個特殊集體。該地區整體主要由新喀里多尼亞島和洛亞蒂群島組成。作爲法國的海外屬地之一，除官方語言法語以外，美拉尼西亞語和玻里尼西亞語亦通用於此。"},{"pid":"6f2657317ab16e21675a29f5213b31043deff4cb","tid":2229418,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:38:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong>半島電視台（Al Jazeera）3日報道，法國總統馬克龍（ Emmanuel Macron）強調歐洲勢力在太平洋地區扮演的角色，以對抗中國逐漸擴大的地緣政治及經濟影響力。惟若新喀里多尼亞獨立，會影響太平洋地區的地緣政治形勢。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4d1dc1fe3e06f26df31f5dee8e4f1d93121500ab","tid":2229418,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:39:58.000Z","msg":"算唔算喀奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd26671433c44c40006c21a5497ca902ec0db548","tid":2229418,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:42:08.000Z","msg":"點解英法聯軍唔打的屬地返來？"},{"pid":"954f5ec128fdd048e0ac4bd49133bfbccc3e6fe2","tid":2229418,"uid":375425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:44:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31104eaa450ac7f4c43e30058cafa98bd526cb92","tid":2229418,"uid":276548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"954f5ec128fdd048e0ac4bd49133bfbccc3e6fe2","tid":2229418,"uid":375425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:44:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:45:55.000Z","msg":"呢D撚屌島國 一有機會就想投共<br />\n最後又係高層貪到肥 平民食屎<br />\n最後就想食回頭草"},{"pid":"7b426fe67a189eaa01432c15a0b2fc28cf2c0c3c","tid":2229418,"uid":37197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"法國仲有一次吊命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca5da652254c3259828c2946fa66412daeea220","tid":2229418,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31104eaa450ac7f4c43e30058cafa98bd526cb92","tid":2229418,"uid":276548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"954f5ec128fdd048e0ac4bd49133bfbccc3e6fe2","tid":2229418,"uid":375425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:44:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:45:55.000Z","msg":"呢D撚屌島國 一有機會就想投共<br />\n最後又係高層貪到肥 平民食屎<br />\n最後就想食回頭草"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:49:32.000Z","msg":"所以好彩(應該)否決咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2bd70916b64dd099157ffcf42dbd7b6156799c",